## Why Look for Northbeam Alternatives?

Northbeam is powerful—ML-driven attribution that prevents over-counting. But it's not right for everyone. (Full disclosure: mbuzz is one of the alternatives we cover. For enterprise DTC brands with massive ad spend and dedicated media buying teams, Northbeam's ML sophistication can be worth it—we'll help you decide.)

**Common reasons to explore alternatives:**

| Limitation | Impact |
|------------|--------|
| **Expensive** | $400+/mo at entry, scales with pageviews—high-traffic sites pay $2-5K+/mo |
| **Steep learning curve** | Complex interface designed for dedicated media buyers |
| **No incrementality** | ML attribution without experimental validation |
| **Black box models** | Can't inspect why Channel A gets 30% vs Channel B's 25% |
| **Enterprise focus** | Overkill for brands under $40M revenue |

If any of these resonate, here are your best options.

